---
entries:
  QL_Water_Relic_Desc:
    - text: "You have been asked to help appease Vah\nRuta, Divine Beast of Water. The task will\nrequire a great many shock arrows.\n\nFind Muzu in "
    - control:
        kind: set_colour
        colour: red
    - text: "Zora's Domain square "
    - control:
        kind: reset_colour
    - text: "to\nfind out where to get them."
  QL_Water_Relic_Finish:
    - text: "You told King Dorephan everything that's\nhappened so far, and now it seems even\nmembers of the Zora's Domain council\nhave accepted you.\n\nYou've also earned one of the Champion's\ncharms, Mipha's Grace.\n\nDivine Beast Vah Ruta has enshrined itself in\npreparation for the battle with Calamity Ganon."
  QL_Water_Relic_Name:
    - text: Divine Beast Vah Ruta
  QL_Water_Relic_Step1:
    - text: "You asked Muzu where to get the arrows, but\nhe refuses to help because you're a Hylian.\nHowever, he seems willing to cooperate if\nyou can somehow prove that you were\nspecial to Mipha.\n\nYou have the "
    - control:
        kind: set_colour
        colour: red
    - text: "Zora armor "
    - control:
        kind: reset_colour
    - text: "that "
    - control:
        kind: set_colour
        colour: red
    - text: "Mipha "
    - control:
        kind: reset_colour
    - text: "made\nfor you. Maybe it will be proof enough."
  QL_Water_Relic_Step1_1:
    - text: "According to Muzu, you can get shock arrows\nfrom Ploymus Mountain.\n\nWearing the Zora armor allows you to "
    - control:
        kind: set_colour
        colour: red
    - text: "swim\nup waterfalls"
    - control:
        kind: reset_colour
    - text: ", so swimming up the waterfall\neast of Zora's Domain will make for a nice\nshortcut.\n\nFirst, you'll need to collect 20 shock arrows."
  QL_Water_Relic_Step1_2:
    - text: "You collected the 20 shock arrows you'll need\nto face the Divine Beast. Now head to\nEast Reservoir Lake and meet with Sidon.\n\nThe lake is "
    - control:
        kind: set_colour
        colour: red
    - text: directly below Shatterback Point
    - control:
        kind: reset_colour
    - text: ",\nthe peak of Ploymus Mountain."
  QL_Water_Relic_Step2:
    - text: "You met up with Sidon at East Reservoir Lake\nand are ready to put those shock arrows to\nuse. Their electricity can "
    - control:
        kind: set_colour
        colour: red
    - text: activate the devices
    - control:
        kind: reset_colour
    - text: "\non Divine Beast Vah Ruta's back."
  QL_Water_Relic_Step3:
    - text: "You met up with Sidon at East Reservoir Lake\nand are ready to put those shock arrows to\nuse. Their electricity can "
    - control:
